parameters: Oh, how beautiful... your body is...

I serve Lady Dorothea, the master of Blood Moon
Castle.
What the hell is going on?!
Do you really think you can defeat me?en(v[263]>=100)

To come this far and defy me with a blade...!
Unforgivable.
It's useless to run away! And... who are you?!

Oh, \v[111]-san... You haven't forgotten about
that incident, have you...?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Ugh... Fine... I'll pretend I didn't see anything
here... Just go away quickly...

\v[111], you came all over my body, didn't you?
Don't you want to do that pleasurable thing again?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Hey, I have a little favor to ask...

I think you can tell just by looking... but I'm
pregnant.

If things continue like this, I might end up
giving birth here. If I end up giving birth to a
human...  Note: The word human is in quotes to
indicate that it may not be a literal translation,
but rather a contextual interpretation based on
the previous translated text.

You're going to lose your magical girl powers,
right? Is that it?

Well, if that's the case, let's get straight to
the point. Please, if I end up giving birth, I
won't be able to fight anymore. Is there any way
you can help me out?

Just when I thought what you were going to say,
it's something like that. There are plenty of
magical girls like you.

I don't know if you're some kind of savior or
what, but I can't treat you specially. It would be
best for you to give birth to the baby and retire
quickly.
Ugh... That's a harsh way to put it.

(By the way... It's really not good to give birth
to a human, huh)
Geez, you're so cold. Hey, hey, look at this.

That's right, there's a possibility that I might
end up giving birth. I wonder what kind of
adorable child will be born.
Just give birth without my knowledge.
What if it's a demon or a magical beast?

It seems that the rule is to dispose of everything
except humans and LoliMon.

You don't seem interested, well, I guess it can't
be helped.
Don't say things like that, it's so cold of you.

What are you saying, even though you're a
criminal? Just because you're a magical girl,
don't think everything will be forgiven.

Geez, you're so cold. Even though I brought a nice
story with me.

I have no intention of listening to the story of a
criminal. Reflect quietly.

Actually... I wanted to convey that I'm very
sorry...

I see. That's all well and good, but conveying
that won't lessen your guilt.

Well, don't say it like that. Despite how I may
appear, I've been reflecting a lot, you know.

I see. That's all well and good, but conveying
that won't lessen the guilt.
Temptation has no effect on us, the vampire clan.

Hey, look, I have five bottles of Blood Wine.
Wouldn't it be amazing if we got drunk on this?

Look at this, five bottles of Blood Wine! I'm sure
it'll make our heads spin and send us flying.

If you let me take it out, I'll secretly give this
only to you... How about it?

How about a deal? If you let me out of here, all
of this will be yours.

Oh my... how sinful... but this is so hard to come
by... I want to taste it... *gulp*

F-Fine... I'll secretly... let you out, so... give
it to me...
Negotiations successful, huh? Well then, go ahead.
Dealing with vampires is indeed tough...
